overview.en: ATK (currency) of charge to an account one-stop digital asset management platform, asset management, financial services open platform of charge to an account, life service platform, encrypted digital wallets, community information, personal information security box, and other functions and integration, is committed to providing customers with concise and easy to use, convenient management tool, for all participants achieve ecological interests and maximize the value of providing a healthy platform.
